This is the cost of the sold goods, which is the cost of the production of the goods, and the storage.

59:39.000 --> 59:47.000
The cost of the production of the goods can include both variable and constant production costs.

59:48.000 --> 59:58.000
The cost of the sold goods is the cost of the variable sold goods and the constant production costs.

