Here, in the profit report, we see the variable commercial costs,

01:00:35.000 --> 01:00:44.000
which also include the variable cost of the sold goods and the variable commercial costs.

01:00:45.000 --> 01:00:48.000
After all, our goal is to group all the variable costs.

01:00:49.000 --> 01:00:53.000
The difference between them will give the marginal profit.

01:00:54.000 --> 01:00:59.000
The marginal profit will be equal to 6,000, and it differs from the value of the volume margin.

