01:01:32.000 --> 01:01:38.000
And in the same way, the constant commercial costs are subtracted from the traditional profit report.

01:01:39.000 --> 01:01:42.000
Why are they subtracted here, despite the fact that they are constant?

01:01:43.000 --> 01:01:47.000
